Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.data_spec

Data specification generator and executor. The main class here is Executor.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FunctionAPI
    The interface supported by the Functions class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    Constants used by the Data Structure Generator (DSG) and the Specification Executor.
    Executor
    Used to execute a SpiNNaker data specification language file to produce a memory image.
    MemoryRegion
    Marker of something that is a memory region.
    MemoryRegionCollection
    A collection of memory regions.
    MemoryRegionReal
    A memory region storage object.
    MemoryRegionReference
    A reference to another region.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Commands
    Set of opcodes for the spec executor.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DataSpecificationException
    Exceptions thrown by the Data Specification code.
    ExecuteBreakInstruction
    A special exception that indicates that a BREAK was encountered.
    NoMoreException
    An exception that indicates that there is no more space for the requested item.
    NoRegionSelectedException
    An exception that indicates that a memory region has not been selected.
    RegionInUseException
    An exception that indicates that a region has already been allocated.
    RegionNotAllocatedException
    An exception which occurs when trying to write to an unallocated region of memory.
    RegionUnfilledException
    An exception that indicates that a memory region is being used that was originally requested to be unfilled.
    UnimplementedDSECommandException
    An exception which occurs when trying to execute an unimplemented command.
    UnknownTypeLengthException
    An exception that indicates that the value of the requested type is unknown.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Operation
    This annotation is used to indicate which methods should be used to implement DSE operations.
